th=598 height=32 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Participate in weekly challenges that emulate the real world championships</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/0215abd08cba020843cc9a298fa94bcf.poster.avif?t=1744213639\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/0215abd08cba020843cc9a298fa94bcf.webm?t=1744213639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/0215abd08cba020843cc9a298fa94bcf.mp4?t=1744213639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Test your skills in dynamic weekly challenges inspired by real-world racing events. Each week brings new tracks, different weather conditions, and unique racing scenarios. Compete for glory, exclusive rewards, and the chance to prove that you have what it takes to be a true champion in both virtual and real racing worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/9f52bf667dba0f109e773496a27e230f.webp?t=1744213639\" width=598 height=32 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overtake on track or strategize your way to victory</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/75643fea4261e87b3efb482bfc3c50a2.poster.avif?t=1744213639\" width=590 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/75643fea4261e87b3efb482bfc3c50a2.webm?t=1744213639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/75643fea4261e87b3efb482bfc3c50a2.mp4?t=1744213639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DRS, pit stops, weather changes—use every tool at your disposal to outsmart and outpace your rivals. Every decision counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/c9d46c86ecf76f3bbe72e997051e2157.webp?t=1744213639\" width=598 height=32 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create your own team and upgrade your facilities </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/84250f350d2cab30a6045f22534f700d.poster.avif?t=1744213639\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/84250f350d2cab30a6045f22534f700d.webm?t=1744213639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/84250f350d2cab30a6045f22534f700d.mp4?t=1744213639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Build and manage your own racing team from the ground up. Develop your headquarters, attract top-tier sponsors, and invest in cutting-edge technology. Upgrade your car's performance, improve your team's efficiency, and turn your fledgling team into a powerhouse. Guide your team through the seasons and aim to become the world champion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/e73ad5972fb73bf3e2500756faed6ad3.webp?t=1744213639\" width=598 height=32 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Design the car you want</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/718cb728395b0c42a8ab7d2aaa9ae59f.poster.avif?t=1744213639\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/718cb728395b0c42a8ab7d2aaa9ae59f.webm?t=1744213639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/718cb728395b0c42a8ab7d2aaa9ae59f.mp4?t=1744213639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Unleash your creativity and  design your perfect race car. Customize every detail of the livery to ensure your vehicle stands out on the track. With endless customization options, you can create a car that not only looks amazing but also delivers peak performance in every race.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/9f52bf667dba0f109e773496a27e230f.webp?t=1744213639\" width=598 height=32 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Climb the ranks online and unlock a ton of rewards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/f7b492230fd814df0d35835101280924.poster.avif?t=1744213639\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/f7b492230fd814df0d35835101280924.webm?t=1744213639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/f7b492230fd814df0d35835101280924.mp4?t=1744213639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Rise through the online leaderboards by competing in intense, skill-based races. Prove your mettle against other players and earn a variety of exciting rewards. Unlock new cars, customizations, and exclusive content as you progress. Can you reach the top and claim the ultimate rewards?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088330/extras/c9d46c86ecf76f3bbe72e997051e2157.webp?t=1744213639\" width=598 height=32 /></span>Enjoy all the great features that make the biggest motorsport ever</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 20+ Tracks from all over the world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Weather changes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Tyre strategies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- DRS management</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- And so much more...</p>",
